1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,000
What if I told you your kidneys play a secret role in your blood pressure?

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:11,200
Meet the renin-angiotensin system, a critical player in regulating blood flow and pressure.

3
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:16,000
When blood pressure drops, kidneys release renin, triggering a cascade of reactions.

4
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:20,400
This process produces angiotensin, which narrows blood vessels and raises pressure.

5
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:25,200
Understanding this system may help manage conditions like hypertension, but it’s complex.

6
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:28,000
Curious about how your body keeps balance?

7
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:30,000
